一般而言變電站需留有通道以便維修<ref name="design"/>，若變電站亦應留有足夠樓底高度<ref name="CLP">{{cite web |author1=CLP |title=COP 101 Distribution Substation Design |url=https://www.clp.com.hk/en/customer-service-site/open-and-close-account-site/cop-101-distribution-substation-design-site/Documents/Cop101%20version%2015%20black%20letters.pdf |accessdate=2020-08-05}}</ref>。某些城市內的變電站則或會稍作修飾以融入當地環境<ref name="House"/>。

